.Nd 
Web Assembler creates complete HTML or XML documents from reusable pieces.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op options
command
.Op Ar file ...
.Nm
.Fl source
path/to/source
.Fl output
path/to/output \fBbuild\fR
.Nm
.Fl config
